Check out this bipartisan report from the Ad Hoc Committee for 2020 Election Fairness & Legitimacy. 

In the report, the members of this esteemed Ad Hoc Committee provide recommendations for how to run "Fair Elections During A Crisis." 

CLICK HERE: https://t.co/5VVeawSBfy

full_text: I wholeheartedly agree with my colleague @repmarkwalker. The @GOPleader and Republicans have emphasized that the House must return to regular order. If Speaker Pelosi and Leader Hoyer want to accuse @realdonaldtrump of inaction, they need to take a long look in the mirror first. https://t.co/uiVE5DMfSB
